<title>
<sentence type="quasi">足利義満</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">（一三五八〜一四〇八）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">・あしかがよしみつ◆<ruby rubyText="きん">金</ruby><ruby rubyText="かく">閣</ruby>をつくる</sentence>
